kattanOS is a GNU/Linux Distribution based on Debian GNU/Linux stable (currently 10.1 as of version 1.0).
Its goal is to provide a ready and easy-to-use and secure Linux Distribution.
kattanOS comes bundled with all expected office and productivity tools such as LibreOffice suite, Firefox and Chrome browsers,
as well as security and anonymity tools such as VeraCrypt and TorBrowser.
kattanOS can be booted directly as a Live system or installed on a physical hardware (with Calamares).
More info here: https://ralphkattan.ch
ralph@ralphkattan.ch
